com.swirl

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.SObject
      • com.swirl.Location
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Config.Location

    public class Location
extends SObject
    A Location represents a physical street, city, state address or real world location. All proximity signals are placed in a Placement within a Location.
